  <summary date="2022-01-13T16:35:05Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Fix Funding First Act

This bill makes several modifications to the federal budget process. Among other modifications, the bill changes the dates of the fiscal year to match the calendar year; requires a biennial budget resolution that is signed into law by the President; and limits congressional pay, recesses, and travel if the budget resolution and the appropriations bills have not been enacted within specified time frames.</summary>
